data.description: Immaculate home in Windstone at Upland addition, 3/2/2 1760 sq.ft of beautiful open concept design. Spacious gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, with undermount sink, lots of cabinet storage, gas stove. Has Reverse Osmosis system for drinking and connection to refrigerator. Living room has wood burning fireplace. Spacious Master bedroom and huge ensuite bathroom with separate soaking tub and shower, separate His/her vanity. HUGE walk-in closet with access from master bath and laundry room. Full guest bathroom. Covered patio. Welcome to your forever home!!
